title: Christian McBride on his early music education & development
description: Bassist Christian McBride talks about his early musical education and development, including his first instrument, his first paid gig and an unusual appearance on daytime TV by Miles Davis. This In Person with JazzTimes interview took place at the 2012 Newport Jazz Festival, where McBride performed with his group Inside Straight. Interview by Lee Mergner. Video by Melissa Mergner. Audio by Jen Kim. Special thanks to Carolyn McClair, Melanie Nanez, Dan Melnick, Deborah Ross and the staff of George Wein Productions.
